act us to make a request regarding such information (including your personal information), please contact us at https://www.bodis.com/contact. In contacting us, you must include the reference to \"Privacy Request\" in the subject line and in the body of the message and include the email address or mailing address, as applicable, for us to send our response. We reserve the right not to respond to inquiries submitted other than at the contact page specified above.",
